#
# Use the following syntax for specifying values for the profiles:
#
#   <tag>:<value>
#   where:
#       <tag> can be one of the following:
#               Provisioning_Tag
#               Mode
#               Content_Category
#
# Use these rules for assigning filter modes:
#
#       Use Modes that are defined in pin_wireless.h
#
# Use these rules for specifying values:
#      You must specify the Root_or_Brand_Tag immediately after the
#       Provisioning_Tag.
#
# When you load profiles using this app, the old profile tag information
# will be replaced by the current values.
#
#       Sample file:
#       #comment
#       #comment
#
